        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer5113792" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16004326734029420120">I am always skeptical about sequels, but this one was amazing. I would say I liked this one even better than My name is Asher Lev. Asher&apos;s a bit older and has a family in this one, so his issues are different. There is a mystery woven throughout this novel pertaining to a riddle that the rabbi shares at Asher&apos;s uncle&apos;s death. A really great book. Highly recommended.</span>
  <span id="freeText16004326734029420120" style="display:none">I am always skeptical about sequels, but this one was amazing. I would say I liked this one even better than My name is Asher Lev. Asher's a bit older and has a family in this one, so his issues are different. There is a mystery woven throughout this novel pertaining to a riddle that the rabbi shares at Asher's uncle's death. A really great book. Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16004326734029420120" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

